Package ohos.agp.components

Class TableLayout.LayoutConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.components.ComponentContainer.LayoutConfig
      • ohos.agp.components.TableLayout.LayoutConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Enclosing class:
    TableLayout

    public static class TableLayout.LayoutConfig
extends ComponentContainer.LayoutConfig
    Provides layout parameters required in a table layout.

    Grid layout parameters integrate ComponentContainer.LayoutConfig and provides the TableLayout.Specification. The former indicates margin layout parameters in the component container, and the latter indicates row and column specifications.

    Since:
    3
